text: Rott is a river of Bavaria, Germany. The Rott springs north of the district of Großkarolinenfeld. It then flows next to Großkarolinenfeld and discharges near Rott am Inn from the left into the Inn. ==See also== *List of rivers of Bavaria ==References== Category:Rivers of Bavaria Category:Rivers of Germany
title: Rott (Inn, Rott am Inn)
